        <script type="text/javascript">

            var APPLICATION_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE = "en";

            var validateFlag = true;
            var JSF_FORM_ID = "loginForm:";
            var numErrorMessages = 0;
            var certificateWarning = false;
            var urlWarning = false;
            var browserWarning = false;
            var doSubmit = true;

            function setTopFrame() {
                var url = "https://pxmwfa02:9443/manager/login/pages/loginPage.jsf";
                if (top.location) {
                    top.location.replace(url);
                } else {
                    top.document.location.replace(url);
                }
            }

            function init() {

                //
                // if we are opened in a popup -> close the window
                //
                if (window.opener) {
                    try {
                        var pageId = window.opener.document.getElementById("whatPageForm:whatPage");
                        if (pageId) {
                            try {
                                window.opener.top.ProcessManager.StopProcessBarInTopFrame();
                            } catch (err) {//alert("cant remove the process bar pane");
                            }
                            try {
                                var refreshButton = window.opener.document.getElementById("idRefreshForm:mainPageContainerRefreshButton");
                                if (refreshButton) {
                                    refreshButton.click();
                                }
                            } catch (err) {//alert("cant refresh main screen");
                            }
                            //
                            // close the window
                            //
                            window.close();
                        } else {//alert("page id does not exist");
                        }
                    } catch (err) {//alert("cant access the opener document "+err.description);
                    }
                }

                //
                // make sure we are displayed out of a frameset
                //
                if (self != top) {
                    setTopFrame();
                }

                //
                // Warn user if his browser does not meet the requirements below:
                //     - Firefox 4 and newer
                //     - Chrome 13 and newer
                //     - IE 8 through 10 (NO Compatibility View)
                //
                var supportedBrowsers = ["Explorer", "Firefox", "Chrome", "Edge"];
                var isSupportedBrowser = false;
                if ((BrowserDetect.browser == "Firefox" && BrowserDetect.version < 4) || (BrowserDetect.browser == "Chrome" && BrowserDetect.version < 13)) {//isSupportedBrowser = false;
                } else {
                    for (var i = 0; i < supportedBrowsers.length; i++) {
                        if (BrowserDetect.browser == supportedBrowsers[i]) {
                            isSupportedBrowser = true;
                            break;
                        }
                    }
                }

                // If IE, continue by checking for version 8-10
                if (isSupportedBrowser && BrowserDetect.isIE()) {
                    BrowserDetect.isIE(11, true);
                    // Note: we do not support Compatibility View (which registers as IE7)
                    isSupportedBrowser = isSupportedBrowser && !BrowserDetect.usingIECompatView();
                }

                if (!isSupportedBrowser) {
                    var objBrowserDetect = document.getElementById(JSF_FORM_ID + "idUnsupportedBrowserWarning");
                    if (objBrowserDetect) {
                        objBrowserDetect.style.display = "list-item";
                        showErrorMesssageContainer(true);
                        numErrorMessages++;
                        browserWarning = true;
                    }
                }

                //
                // check for underscore in the URL
                //
                var urlPath = "https://pxmwfa02:9443/manager/login/";
                if (urlPath.indexOf("_") != -1) {
                    //var objURLDetect = document.getElementById("loginForm:urlDetectText");
                    var objURLDetect = document.getElementById(JSF_FORM_ID + "idURLDetect");
                    if (objURLDetect) {
                        objURLDetect.style.display = "list-item";
                        showErrorMesssageContainer(true);
                        numErrorMessages++;
                        urlWarning = true;
                    }
                }

                //
                // calculate warning messages text
                //
                if (numErrorMessages != 0) {
                    var objWarningTitle = document.getElementById(JSF_FORM_ID + "idWarningTitle");
                    if (objWarningTitle) {
                        objWarningTitle.innerHTML = "You have " + numErrorMessages + " warning message(s)";
                    }
                }

                document.forms['loginForm'].elements['loginForm:idUserName'].placeholder = "User name";

                document.forms['loginForm'].elements['loginForm:idPassword'].placeholder = "Password";

                //
                // set the focus on the username field
                //
                document.forms['loginForm'].reset();
                if (!false && !false) {
                    document.forms['loginForm'].elements['loginForm:idUserName'].value = "";
                }
                if (!false) {
                    document.forms['loginForm'].elements['loginForm:idUserName'].focus();
                }

            }

            function showErrorMesssageContainer(show) {
                var objWarningContainer = document.getElementById("warningContainer");
                if (objWarningContainer) {
                    if (show) {
                        objWarningContainer.style.display = "block";
                    } else {
                        objWarningContainer.style.display = "none";
                        numErrorMessages = 0;
                    }
                }
            }

            //dummy function to avoid js error - do not remove
            function getScrolling() {
                //do nothing
                return ""
            }

            function beforeSubmit() {
                if (!doSubmit) {
                    return false;
                }
                if (validateFlag) {
                    if (validateForm()) {
                        doSubmit = false;
                        //no double submit
                        return true;
                    } else {
                        return false;
                    }
                } else {
                    doSubmit = false;
                    //no double submit
                    return true;
                }
            }

            //
            //Set the error container to visibile
            //
            function setErrorSectionVisibility() {
                showHideErrorElement("errorContainer", true);
                showHideErrorElement("pageErrorDivContainer", true);
            }

            //
            //Clean all errors
            //
            function resetErrorContainer() {
                //
                // remove the already existing errors
                //
                var errorContainer = document.getElementById("pageErrorDivContainer");
                var errorTable = errorContainer.getElementsByTagName("Table")[0];
                if (errorTable != undefined && errorTable.hasChildNodes()) {
                    while (errorTable.childNodes.length >= 1) {
                        errorTable.removeChild(errorTable.firstChild);
                    }
                }

                //
                // hide the page error
                //
                showHideErrorElement("errorContainer", false);
                showHideErrorElement("pageErrorDivContainer", false);
            }

            function validateForm() {

                var errMsgClassName = "lgErrorMessage";
                ErrorManager.init(errMsgClassName);

                var username = JSF_FORM_ID + "idUserName";
                ErrorManager.validateFieldNotEmpty(username, "Please enter a user name.");

                var password = JSF_FORM_ID + "idPassword";
                if (ErrorManager.formValidated) {
                    ErrorManager.validateFieldNotEmpty(password, "Please enter a password.");
                }

                var isvalid = ErrorManager.finalize();
                if (!isvalid) {
                    showHideErrorElement("errorContainer", true);
                    showHideErrorElement("pageErrorDivContainer", true);
                }

                return isvalid;
            }

            function showHideErrorElement(elementId, isShow) {
                var className = 'visibilityHidden';
                if (isShow === true) {
                    className = 'visibilityVisible';
                }
                var element = document.getElementById(elementId);
                if (element) {
                    element.className = className;
                }
            }

            function submitWithValidation() {
                validateFlag = true;
            }

            function submitWithoutValidation() {
                validateFlag = false;
            }

            function openDialogWindowForCertificateWarningInfo() {
                Richfaces.showModalPanel('notificationInfoPanel');
            }

            function hideDialogWindowForCertificateWarningInfo() {
                Richfaces.hideModalPanel('notificationInfoPanel');
            }

            function openCertificateInstallPage() {

                var winURL = "https://pxmwfa02:9443/manager-help/certificateSupport/installCertificate.html";
                window.location.href = winURL;
            }

            function showLoginWarningsDialog() {
                var objWarningContainer;

                if (certificateWarning) {
                    objWarningContainer = document.getElementById("logonWarningsInfoForm:idCertificateWarningDetail");
                    objWarningContainer.style.display = "block";
                }
                if (urlWarning) {
                    objWarningContainer = document.getElementById("logonWarningsInfoForm:idURLDetectDetail");
                    objWarningContainer.style.display = "block";
                }
                if (browserWarning) {
                    objWarningContainer = document.getElementById("logonWarningsInfoForm:idUnsupportedBrowserWarningDetail");
                    objWarningContainer.style.display = "block";
                }

                Richfaces.showModalPanel('logonWarningsInfoPanel');
            }

            function closeLoginWarningsDialog() {
                Richfaces.hideModalPanel('logonWarningsInfoPanel');
            }

            function showPasswordRecoveryDialog() {
                Richfaces.showModalPanel('passwordRecoveryInfoPanel');
            }

            function closePasswordRecoveryDialog() {
                Richfaces.hideModalPanel('passwordRecoveryInfoPanel');
            }

            function showGeneralHelpWindow(localizationHint) {
                if (localizationHint == null || localizationHint == '') {
                    if (window.APPLICATION_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE && APPLICATION_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE.length > 0) {
                        localizationHint = APPLICATION_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE;
                    } else {
                        localizationHint = 'en';
                    }
                }
                var baseUrl = "https://pxmwfa02:9443/triton-help%s/wwhelp/wwhimpl/common/html/wwhelp.htm#href=logon.htm";
                baseUrl = baseUrl.replace("%s", "/" + localizationHint);
                window.open(baseUrl, "helpWindow");
            }

            function showRsaHelpWindow(localizationHint) {
                if (localizationHint == null || localizationHint == '') {
                    if (window.APPLICATION_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE && APPLICATION_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE.length > 0) {
                        localizationHint = APPLICATION_DEFAULT_LANGUAGE;
                    } else {
                        localizationHint = 'en';
                    }
                }
                var baseUrl = "https://pxmwfa02:9443/triton-help%s/wwhelp/wwhimpl/common/html/wwhelp.htm#href=rsa_auth.htm";
                baseUrl = baseUrl.replace("%s", "/" + localizationHint);
                window.open(baseUrl, "helpWindow");
            }

            function openBrowsersWarningDialog() {
                Richfaces.showModalPanel('browsersWarningPanel');
            }

            function attempt2FALogin() {
                try {
                    document.execCommand("ClearAuthenticationCache");
                } catch (e) {/* FF it's ok*/
                }
                window.location.href = "/manager/";
            }
        </script>
